Important information

Indications

Ileum, colon, rectum, urethrostomy

Directions

1. Open packaging, 2. Clean stoma area, 3. Select and cut pouch size, 4. Apply pouch, 5. Ensure seal and empty as needed.

Legal Disclaimer

PRECAUTION (1) The film configured with this product is recommended to be pasted for 3-5 days. Excessive use will affect the pasting effect, lead to shedding or leakage, and may cause skin damage; (2) If the bag has flatulence, please use a needle to pierce the upper end of the bag to exhaust the air. It is recommended to use an activated carbon filter to stick it on the exhaust hole to remove the odor; (3) Do not directly flush the used ostomy bag into the toilet and sewer, in order to avoid blockage, do not discard it carelessly, please put it in the trash can, and pay attention to environmental protection. (4) People with skin allergy to viscose should use it with caution. If skin irritation occurs during use, please stop using it immediately and consult a medical professional.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
